Move: ASD/Arrows
Jump: W/Up
Hit Slime: Left Click (when close)
Move Bat: Right Click
Menu: SpaceBar

When Mage or Bat hits slime, use cursor to aim. 

Deliver slime to Daddy Slime, at the top of the map!
